<div type="definition">
<p>DEVELOP OR CHANGE so as to BECOME MORE EXCELLENT.</p>
<p>[[FORTSCHRITT]]</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. The current general word denoting progress of any kind is yì 益.</p>
<p>2. Jìn 進 is very occasionally used to denote progress.</p>
        </div>
